Texts.Chs:
不知怎的，你把以太给烤成面包了。它能够帮助你避开黑暗和阴影。 好味。
赋予^pink;暗影污染^gray;，^pink;黑暗^cyan;免疫^gray;(^white;持续90s^gray;)^reset;
Texts.Eng:
Somehow, raw celestial essence has been baked. It should stave off darkness and shadow, too. Yummo.
^pink;Shadow^gray;, ^pink;Darkness ^cyan;Immunity ^gray;(^white;90s^gray;)^reset;
